reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful soft fitted sweater
reviews.reviewText: I love the fit I love the softness I have this sweater in almost every color it comes in and get compliments every time I wear them

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 16, 2022
reviews.reviewText: When I later this out I thought oh no it’s way too big! I wear a medium to a large depending on the item. This is a large and it fits perfect because the material is stretchy. I don’t like shirts too big so I like that it’s comfortable (not too tight) but form fitting because of the material, which by the way is very soft!! The sleeves are a good length and the stitching is good, the buttons are sown well and it’s not too low cut. If you wear a large normally you might consider buying the next size up. The only semi bad thing I have to say is, this color was described as red I could tell from the picture that it Was more of a rust color (which I love) so be careful choosing your color.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 2, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice sweater-color description not accurate
reviews.reviewText: This is a nice, well made, lightweight soft sweater. The fit was perfect, usually order a large and the large fit exactly as expected. The color description was red, but the picture looked more like a brown. I ordered it hoping the picture was was wrong, but the picture was spot on. It’s more of a brown/caramel color. I’m disappointed it’s not red, but it’s still a pretty sweater so no harm done.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Color is not as described!
reviews.reviewText: I bought the Red, this is a rusty brown, very disappointed. The fit is good and the material is soft. I'm 5'3 and 105 lbs, bust 36, and the medium fits good. Just very disappointed with the color.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This is a really nice sweater, it's flattering and made from a nice material. I ordered my usual size medium and it fits well. I like the button details so I don't just have another black sweater for my collection.5'3, 150lbs, 32F, usually a medium ordered a medium

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 6, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Steel blue sweater
reviews.reviewText: I ordered this sweater in blue, which is really a cool steel looking blue. I got the large since I usually wear tops in size 10/12. It fits well ( disregard my Thanksgiving belly rolls please).The material is very soft, the buttons look fashionable and they are all stitched on well, nothing has fallen off yet. I washed it on cold and dried on very low, it came out perfect and did not shrink or lose its shape. I do recommend this sweater - the quality is great, seams are well sewn, no snags, no threads and it is not your run of the mill style.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 2, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The perfect cool/cold weather pullover top
reviews.reviewText: I got this top in red and a Size L. The red is actually a muted brick color which I find a soothing fall-neutral, and the Size L fits perfectly true-to-size. The material is a wide-ribbed knit that feels luxurious against the skin, and the Henley-style V-neck gives this top a nice finished look. It's medium-weight enough to fit comfortably beneath a jacket on colder days, or to wear alone atop jeans or leggings when the weather is cool, but not cold. I'm very pleased with this top.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 22, 2022
reviews.reviewText: This says red on the site and on the bag it came in, but it is more brown than red. I don't like this color. But the sweater is well made and feels good on. If they get a real red I would buy it.
